1
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,080
All our sorrows.

2
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,120
Zhaoxue.

3
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:21,760
Are you ready?

4
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,320
I've been ready.

5
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,720
I've been waiting for ages.

6
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:25,560
Let's go.

7
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:26,680
Wait.

8
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,760
My leg hurts a bit today.

9
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:36,840
I'm kidding.

10
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,500
You're actually carrying me?

11
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:06,440
At a time like this,

12
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,580
you're still messing around?

13
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:16,240
We all know we might not make it back.

14
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:18,560
They just won't say it out loud.

15
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,360
If we don't get close now,

16
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:24,560
should we wait until we're dead?

17
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:40,560
I, Fang Ji, Imperial Censor, have returned from Jinzhou.

18
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,100
I have an urgent matter

19
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,920
to report to His Majesty.

20
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,160
His Majesty is discussing important matters with Chancellor Qin.

21
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:49,090
Please come back later, Lord Fang.

22
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:49,890
How dare you!

23
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,920
Here is the token bestowed by the Emperor.

24
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,120
Kneel before it!

25
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,780
Greetings, Imperial Censor.

26
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,760
Go announce me.

27
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:03,280
Yes.

28
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:09,120
Where did you get that token?

29
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:10,760
It's fake.

30
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:14,320
That is the crime of deceiving the Emperor.

31
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:17,120
After I see the Emperor and bring down State Preceptor Qin,

32
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,360
and avenge my father,

33
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,970
I will confess my crime to the Emperor.

34
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,000
Lord Fang.

35
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,260
His Majesty knows of your return.

36
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:32,320
But he is discussing important matters with the State Preceptor.

37
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:33,850
He ordered me to lead the way

38
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:36,250
and take you to the Imperial Study.

39
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:36,970
Let's go.

40
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:37,840
Wait.

41
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:46,520
Fang Ji is a convicted criminal.

42
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,280
Why go to the Imperial Study?

43
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,880
You may leave.

44
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:53,640
Yes.

45
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,720
What are you waiting for?

46
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:59,890
Come with me to see His Majesty at once.

47
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:59,640
Alright.

48
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:05,680
Let's go.

49
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,080
Let's go.

50
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:29,600
I have always regarded Fang Yu as a trusted aide.

51
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:32,240
But he had ulterior motives.

52
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:36,240
He even plotted conspiracies right under my nose,

53
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,920
disrupting the court.

54
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,600
What do you think?

55
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:54,560
I believe Fang Yu's crimes are unpardonable.

56
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:56,760
To warn others,

57
00:04:57,000 --> 00:05:00,120
he should be publicly executed

58
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,730
to show the Imperial power.

59
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:07,840
It will also warn other officials

60
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:13,560
and the commoners against dissent.

61
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:18,360
Only then can the court be stabilized

62
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:21,840
and the peace of our dynasty maintained.

63
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,440
You are quite right.

64
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,120
I share the same view.

65
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:35,760
However, I have thought it over.

66
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:40,280
Although Fang Yu's crimes are heinous,

67
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:44,360
he has a good reputation among the people.

68
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:48,080
If executed rashly,

69
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:53,040
it might cause turmoil in the court.

70
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:58,480
I have already...

71
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:00,640
Your Majesty.

72
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,280
I have already...

73
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,130
Your Majesty, wait.

74
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:12,410
Beware of being deceived by treacherous ministers.

75
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,520
How dare you!

76
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:17,360
Who are you?

77
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:25,160
She is the eldest daughter of Su Ziliang, the witchcraft criminal from ten years ago.

78
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:29,360
She's the one who slipped through the net during the Su family purge ten years ago.

79
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:33,240
She hates the royal family for what happened back then,

80
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:35,120
so she conspired with the Fang family

81
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:38,520
to wreak havoc with witchcraft.

82
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,240
Qin Heng.

83
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:44,880
Ten years ago, His Majesty was deceived by treacherous officials like you.

84
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:47,880
You framed my father and had my whole family executed.

85
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,400
I was lucky enough to escape,

86
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:53,240
just to find a chance to clear my father's name.

87
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:58,640
Your Majesty, I have evidence here.

88
00:06:58,640 --> 00:06:59,960
The rights and wrongs...

89
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:02,680
...will be clear once you read this.

90
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,280
Present it.

91
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:12,500
Please examine it, Your Majesty.

92
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:50,880
This is Consort Shu's handwriting.

93
00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:52,120
This is...

94
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:54,520
This is Consort Shu's handwriting.

95
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:59,040
Su Zhaoxue forged this.

96
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,920
She colluded with the Fang family

97
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,840
to mislead you.

98
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:06,280
Your Majesty, do not fall for her trick.

99
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:07,320
I,

100
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:10,120
Jian Boning, Prefect of Jinzhou,

101
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,690
greet Your Majesty.

102
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:14,920
Your Majesty,

103
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,600
it has been verified that

104
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:19,960
Imperial Preceptor Qin and Lu Shen, Governor of Shuoyuan,

105
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:22,860
engaged in corruption and formed factions,

106
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,930
and murdered court officials.

107
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:25,760
Humph.

108
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:27,760
Sheer nonsense.

109
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:30,320
Your Majesty,

110
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:35,320
I obtained these ledgers from Lu Shen,

111
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,299
which record in detail...

112
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:41,679
Here is the correspondence between him and Director Qin Heng

113
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:44,159
from the past ten years.

114
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:47,080
Please take a look, Your Majesty.

115
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,330
He is the mastermind

116
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:09,440
who framed Lord Su Ziliang's family ten years ago.

117
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:25,840
So you are that clerk from back then,

118
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,300
Dian Ma.

119
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:29,200
Didn't they say you died in an accident?

120
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:32,080
How dare you, after Consort Shu entered the palace,

121
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:34,120
still exchange letters with her,

122
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:37,650
and even plot to help her fake her death to escape?

123
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,560
You are truly presumptuous.

124
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:46,760
So Your Majesty still remembers stealing another man's wife.

125
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,960
I changed my name,

126
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:51,600
assumed a new identity,

127
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:53,400
and climbed my way up step by step

128
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:57,120
just for this day.

129
00:09:58,520 --> 00:09:59,320
Your Majesty,

130
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:04,280
the nineteen-year grudge for stealing my wife,

131
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:06,320
it is time to settle it.

132
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,560
You never imagined

133
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:36,880
that the lowly clerk who couldn't even get an audience

134
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:44,440
would one day become your right-hand man, did you?

135
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:50,960
You were behind the witchcraft case ten years ago too, weren't you?

136
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:59,400
The witchcraft ten years ago never existed.

137
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:02,800
The harem simply saw you were sickly

138
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:05,840
and were jealous of Lady Meng's favor,

139
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:10,640
so they made it up to frame her.

140
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:11,560
So,

141
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:16,100
when my father investigated the case on His Majesty's orders,

142
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:19,600
it was because he discovered the affair between you and Consort Shu.

143
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,720
To save yourself,

144
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:25,040
you colluded with others to frame my father as the culprit.

145
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:26,280
Exactly.

146
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:31,400
Lord Su was a smart man.

147
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:34,720
It's a pity.

148
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,000
was too righteous

149
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:35,160
He

150
00:11:36,160 --> 00:11:38,090
and didn't know how to be flexible.

151
00:11:38,760 --> 00:11:42,720
If he had been willing to cooperate with me,

152
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:47,400
his whole family wouldn't have been executed.

153
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,440
You traitor!

154
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:51,400
My father served the country and people his whole life.

155
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:53,060
Why did you have to harm him so?

156
00:11:53,280 --> 00:11:54,680
How do you sleep at night?

157
00:11:54,920 --> 00:11:56,520
You went to such great lengths

158
00:11:56,520 --> 00:11:58,880
to wreak havoc on the world with witchcraft.

159
00:11:58,880 --> 00:12:01,840
These officials are corrupt.

160
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:04,740
They only care about promotions and wealth.

161
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:08,560
They don't care about the Great Li Dynasty at all,

162
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:10,600
or you, Your Majesty.

163
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:14,920
Otherwise, how could I have persuaded them?

164
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:17,040
What about Fang Ji's mother?

165
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:18,800
She's your own sister!

166
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:20,680
How did she offend you,

167
00:12:20,680 --> 00:12:22,760
for you to harm her like this?

168
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:29,400
Fang Ji.

169
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:35,920
I didn't mean to frame your mother back then.

170
00:12:36,920 --> 00:12:42,840
She just happened to see the letters between Mengniang and me.

171
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:47,160
But she insisted on telling Fang Yu.

172
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:50,400
During our argument,

173
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:54,120
she fell into the water by accident.

174
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:58,600
If Fang Yu hadn't been so focused on work

175
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:01,160
and neglected his sister,

176
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:03,440
she wouldn't have been left in the water

177
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,040
without being found in time.

178
00:13:05,920 --> 00:13:06,920
Qin Heng.

179
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:10,520
She's your own sister.

180
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:12,840
How could you bring yourself to do it?

181
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:17,880
Qin Heng.

182
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:22,760
You are so ruthless.

183
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:26,240
Aren't you afraid of divine retribution?

184
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,640
Divine retribution?

185
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:36,560
Years ago, you used trumped-up charges

186
00:13:36,760 --> 00:13:39,400
to make me execute Mengniang with my own hands.

187
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:44,000
Did you never think that you would face retribution?

188
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:46,120
What a pity.

189
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,880
It was so close.

190
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:54,720
If you had ordered me to behead the Fang father and son in public,

191
00:13:55,560 --> 00:13:57,560
with public grievances boiling over,

192
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:59,360
and witchcraft descending upon the world,

193
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:03,240
you would have been a sinner for all eternity.

194
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:12,600
But it doesn't matter.

195
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:14,400
Today,

196
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:18,120
I'll kill you myself

197
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:22,400
and everyone else here.

198
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:27,400
Then I'll slaughter the world in your name.

199
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:32,640
You'll still go down in history as a sinner.

200
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:37,160
The common people are innocent.

201
00:14:37,800 --> 00:14:40,800
Mother's spirit wouldn't want you to commit more sins.

202
00:14:40,800 --> 00:14:41,800
Stop this.

203
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:45,360
Stop this.

204
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:53,360
Uncle.

205
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:56,440
You've gone too far.

206
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,240
Turn back.

207
00:14:58,520 --> 00:15:00,920
There may still be a chance for redemption.

208
00:15:01,040 --> 00:15:01,840
Ruilang.

209
00:15:04,040 --> 00:15:07,440
This dynasty is rotten to the core.

210
00:15:08,160 --> 00:15:12,840
Only blood can wash this filthy land clean.
